About Me

Plasman Héloïse
2021-04-14

Hi,

I’m Héloïse Plasman, I’m in second grade in Biology in the Univerty of Mons in Belgium. My English teacher this year is Bénédicte Bouchet, I’m in group 4.

I aways like Sciences in general since a long time. That’s why I was already studying Sciences in secondary school.

I have also had English courses since I was in kinder garden because I was in a immersion school.

Besides studies my big passion is pastry and cooking in general. It helps me destress.
